        "generatedLyrics": "[Intro]\n\n[Verse]\nDusty dashboard, sunbeams bright\nWindow down, a perfect sight\nFurry shadow on my lap\nChasing dreams, no turning back\nLittle paws on faded jeans\nLiving out our summer scenes\n\n[Pre-Chorus]\nRadio hums a distant tune\nUnderneath the afternoon\nWish this feeling could just stay\nForever on our getaway\n\n[Chorus]\nOh, the purrs and the open road\nA story only we are told\nSun-drenched whiskers, a gentle sigh\nAs the world goes rushing by\n\n[Verse]\nFields of green, a blur of speed\nEvery moment that we need\nHeads out the window, wind in fur\nA happy, contented purr\nMapping out the miles ahead\nNo place else I'd rather be instead\n\n[Pre-Chorus]\nStreetlights start to paint the sky\nAs the golden hours fly\nWish this feeling could just stay\nForever on our getaway\n\n[Chorus]\nOh, the purrs and the open road\nA story only we are told\nSun-drenched whiskers, a gentle sigh\nAs the world goes rushing by\n\n[Bridge]\nLittle paws kneading the seat\nEvery journey feels so sweet\nNo destination, just the ride\nWith my feline friend by my side\n\n[Instrumental]\n\n[Chorus]\nOh, the purrs and the open road\nA story only we are told\nSun-drenched whiskers, a gentle sigh\nAs the world goes rushing by\n\n[Outro]",
